561
00:45:58,214 --> 00:45:59,424
Conte comigo.

562
00:46:54,854 --> 00:46:57,023
John!

563
00:46:57,106 --> 00:46:59,526
Sou eu. Danny.

564
00:46:59,609 --> 00:47:00,652
Danny?

565
00:47:01,236 --> 00:47:02,570
